      "content": "ive been traveling for months now... seen the ruins in rome, the lights in tokyo, everything i ever put on my bucket list. but honestly? it feels like i'm just checking boxes. everything feels so heavy and empty lately. like i've reached the end of the map and there's nothing left to see. i'm just so tired of the journey.",
